T1  - Acupuncture improves the emotion domain and lipid profiles in women with polycystic ovarian syndrome: a secondary analysis of a randomized clinical trial.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.3389/fendo.2023.1237260
A1  - Chang, Hui
A1  - Shi, Baichao
A1  - Ge, Hang
A1  - Liu, Chengdong
