T1  - The Role of Psychotherapy in the Treatment of Patients with Non- alcoholic Fatty Liver Disease and Obstructive Sleep Apnea.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.15403/jgld-3758
A1  - Filipovic, Branka F
A1  - Latas, Milan
A1  - Kiurski, Stanimir
A1  - Al Kiswani, Dezbal
A1  - Filipovic, Natasa
A1  - Marjanovic-Haljilji, Marija
A1  - Laketic, Darko
A1  - Aksic, Milan
