T1  - Nonalcoholic Fatty Liver Disease and Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus: A Bidirectional Relationship.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1155/2020/6638306
A1  - Muzica, Cristina M
A1  - Sfarti, Catalin
A1  - Trifan, Anca
A1  - Zenovia, Sebastian
A1  - Cuciureanu, Tudor
A1  - Nastasa, Robert
A1  - Huiban, Laura
A1  - Cojocariu, Camelia
