T1  - A Polygenic and Phenotypic Risk Prediction for Polycystic Ovary Syndrome Evaluated by Phenome-Wide Association Studies.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1210/clinem/dgz326
A1  - Joo, Yoonjung Yoonie
A1  - Actkins, Ky'Era
