T1  - Neural respiratory drive and cardiac function in patients with obesity hypoventilation syndrome following initiation of non-invasive ventilation.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.21037/jtd.2017.12.129
A1  - Onofri, Angelo
A1  - Patout, Maxime
A1  - Kaltsakas, Georgios
A1  - Lhuillier, Elodie
A1  - Mushemi-Blake, Sitali
A1  - Arbane, Gill
