T1  - A wireless patch for sleep respiratory disorders applications.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1109/EMBC.2015.7318847
A1  - Gerbelot, R
A1  - Koenig, A
A1  - Goyer, C
A1  - Willemin, J
